tweet: "A chemical sunscreen really just protects against UB – the burning rays. In two hours that’s degraded by the sun. The mineral block [physical sunscreen] is the much better block because it protects against both UVA and UVP," said Dr. Percec. Learn more:  http://bit.ly/2KeSQDu
